name: Waypoint
description: The waypoint the data was collected at.

name: Zone
description: The specific zone of the ocean where the data was collected at.

name: Lat
description: The latitude where the data was collected.

name: Long
description: The longitude where the data was collected.

name: Site
description: The particular site where the data was collected. Data was collected at Black Point (BP) and Wailupe (W).

name: Season
description: The current season at the time of data collection. (SPRING/FALL).

name: Tide_time
description: The current state of the tide at the time of data collection (High/Low) and the time of day (Day/Night).

name: Temp_in
description: The temperature of the ocean at the time of data collection. Measured in Celsius (°C).

name: Salinity
description: The salinity of the ocean at the time of data collection.

name: Phosphate
description: The phosphate concentration of the ocean at the time of data collection.

name: Silicate
description: The silicate concentration of the ocean at the time of data collection.

name: NN
description: The nitrate + nitrite (NN) concentrations of the ocean at the time of data collection.

name: pH
description: The pH of the ocean at the time of data collection.

name: TA
description: The total alkalinity (TA) of the ocean at the time of data collection.

name: percent_sgd
description: The percentage of submarine groundwater discharge (SGD) in the ocean at the time of data collection.
